# Synced tool configs (generated by distill.py — don't commit per-user installs)
# NOTE: .bak files are user-specific backups; the repo ships canon, not generated configs.
# The entire generated tool directories are ignored — they are per-machine deploy targets,
# not source. The source lives in distill/ and core/. Re-run `python scripts/distill.py` to
# regenerate them on any machine.
.agents/

